<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
        <title>About Us | Prakarsh 2026</title>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="college-bg"></div>

        <div class="page-wrapper">
            <div class="lamination">
            <main class="document">
                <div class="document-body">
                    <header>
                        <span class="cert-title">REF: PRK-2026-V1 // CLASS: PUBLIC DOMAIN</span>
                        <h1>Memorandum of Innovation</h1>
                        <div class="ornament"></div>
                    </header>

                    <article class="text-content">
                        <p>
                            <strong>THIS COMPACT</strong> is executed for <strong>PRAKARSH 2026</strong>, 
                            under the aegis of ISTE, between The Central Committee (SVIT) 
                            (hereinafter "The Architects") and The Participant (hereinafter "The Visionary").
                        </p>
                        
                        <p>THE PARTIES HEREBY AGREE TO THE FOLLOWING:</p>

                        <p><strong>ARTICLE I: THE MISSION</strong></p>
                        <p>
                            The Architects covenant to provide a national-level platform driven by 
                            the motto "Ignite Minds and Showcase Skills." The objective 
                            is to bridge the gap between theoretical knowledge and practical 
                            application, empowering The Visionary to venture into the unknown.
                        </p>

                        <p><strong>ARTICLE II: THE DUAL MANDATE (Techfest & Talkfest)</strong></p>
                        <p>The event shall operate as a dynamic two-day nexus offering:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>
                                <strong>Technical Excellence:</strong> A landscape of 
                                workshops, robotics, and prototyping to foster hands-on engineering skills.
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <strong>Holistic Growth:</strong> A blend of elocution, 
                                cultural initiatives, and social awareness to ensure the development 
                                of a well-rounded individual.
                            </li>
                        </ul>

                        <p><strong>ARTICLE III: THE ATMOSPHERE CLAUSE</strong></p>
                        <p>
                            It is agreed that the campus shall be transformed into a hub of Inspiration, 
                            Confidence, and Entertainment. The Architects guarantee an 
                            environment where intellect meets motivation, drawing participants 
                            from diverse regions to interact, compete, and innovate.
                        </p>
                    </article>

                    <footer>
                        <p class="witness-text">IN WITNESS WHEREOF, we pledge to make Prakarsh 2026 a resounding success.</p>
                        <div class="signature">Prakarsh25</div>
                        <p>(Signed) The Architects</p>
                        <div class="signature-line"></div>
                    </footer>
                </div>
                <div class="logo"></div>
            </main>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>

<style>
    /* Reset & Core */
    * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
    }

    body {
        margin: 0;
        background-color: #000;
        font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; /* Traditional document feel */
    }
    .logo{
        position: absolute;
        top: 50%;
        left: 50%;
        width: 75%;
        opacity: .1;
        aspect-ratio: 3/2.72;
        background-image: url('../assets/logo.svg');
        background-size: contain;
        background-repeat: no-repeat;
        background-position: center;
        z-index: 1;
        transform: translate(-50%,-50%) scale(1.1);
    }
    /* 16:9 Fixed Background */
    .college-bg {
        position: fixed;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100vh;
        background-image: url('../assets/svitCollege1.avif');
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;
        filter: blur(2px) brightness(0.5);
        z-index: -1;
        transform: scale(1.1);
    }

    /* Scroll Wrapper */
    .page-wrapper {

        width: 100%;
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 40px 15px; /* Padding for mobile edges */
    }

    /* The Document Component */
    .document {
        background: #fdfdfd;
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 800px;
        /* Logic: 3:4 ratio min-height, but allow growth if text overflows */
        min-height: calc(800px * 4 / 3); 
        box-shadow: 0 40px 100px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
        position: relative;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
    }
    .lamination{
        border-radius: 20px;
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 800px;
        border:50px solid  rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.171);
    }
    @media (max-width:477px) {
    .lamination{
 
        border:10px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.171);
    }
    }

    .document-body {
        padding: 10% 8%;
        flex-grow: 1;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        
    }

    /* Typography & Design Elements */
    header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .cert-title {
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 2px;
        color: #666;
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    h1 {
        font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 5vw, 2.5rem);
        color: #1a1a1a;
        margin: 5px 0;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
    }

    .ornament {
        width: 100px;
        height: 3px;
        background: #c5a059; /* Gold accent */
        margin: 20px auto;
    }

    .text-content p {
        font-size: clamp(1rem, 3vw, 1.15rem);
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        color: #222;
        text-align: justify;
    }

    /* New List Styling for Article II */
    .text-content ul {
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        padding-left: 2rem;
    }

    .text-content li {
        font-size: clamp(1rem, 3vw, 1.15rem);
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
        color: #222;
        padding-left: 0.5rem;
    }

    footer {
        margin-top: auto;
        padding-top: 50px;
        text-align: right;
    }

    .witness-text {
        text-align: center; 
        font-style: italic; 
        margin-bottom: 40px; 
        font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    /* REPLACED SEAL WITH SIGNATURE STYLING */
    .signature {
        font-family: 'Brush Script MT', 'Segoe Script', cursive; /* Handwritten font stack */
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        color: #1a1a1a; /* Dark ink color */
        margin-left: auto; /* Push to right */
        width: fit-content;
        margin-bottom: -15px; /* Overlap the line slightly for realism */
        margin-right: 10px;
        transform: rotate(-10deg); /* Slight angle for authentic look */
        opacity: 0.9;
    }

    .signature-line {
        width: 200px;
        height: 1px;
        background: #000;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-top: 8px;
    }

    /* Responsive Override for Small Screens */
    @media (max-width: 800px) {
        .document {
            min-height: auto;
            aspect-ratio: auto; 
        }
        
        .page-wrapper {
            padding: 20px 10px;
        }

        .document-body {
            padding: 40px 25px;
        }
    }
</style>